    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "annot-g5mujcnc4wql",
      "x": 60,
      "y": 860,
      "width": 705.6,
      "height": 144,
      "text": "AS-BUILT 2026-07-11 (shared legal corpus): the knowledge vault/index gains ONE reserved read-only\npartition `_shared` (SHARED_ORG_ID) holding the public legal corpus (legislacao + jurisprudencia),\nwritten ONLY by the offline importer CLI (api/scripts/migrate/knowledge). Every org search now\nconsults orgId IN (caller, '_shared'); reads fall back org -> shared (org doc shadows shared).\nService writes REFUSE the shared actor (403). New knowledge_doc_map side table maps\n(orgId, collection, docId) -> fts rowid so index deletes are O(log n), not O(corpus);\nbulkIndexDocs() batches the 500k-doc import. The \"never pool across orgs\" rule keeps holding\nfor ORG data - the shared partition is a deliberate, read-only public spine, not org pooling.",
      "originalText": "AS-BUILT 2026-07-11 (shared legal corpus): the knowledge vault/index gains ONE reserved read-only\npartition `_shared` (SHARED_ORG_ID) holding the public legal corpus (legislacao + jurisprudencia),\nwritten ONLY by the offline importer CLI (api/scripts/migrate/knowledge). Every org search now\nconsults orgId IN (caller, '_shared'); reads fall back org -> shared (org doc shadows shared).\nService writes REFUSE the shared actor (403). New knowledge_doc_map side table maps\n(orgId, collection, docId) -> fts rowid so index deletes are O(log n), not O(corpus);\nbulkIndexDocs() batches the 500k-doc import. The \"never pool across orgs\" rule keeps holding\nfor ORG data - the shared partition is a deliberate, read-only public spine, not org pooling.",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#b45309",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 531756059,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 1067500550,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "groupIds": [],
      "boundElements": null,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "containerId": null,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "rawText": "AS-BUILT 2026-07-11 (shared legal corpus): the knowledge vault/index gains ONE reserved read-only\npartition `_shared` (SHARED_ORG_ID) holding the public legal corpus (legislacao + jurisprudencia),\nwritten ONLY by the offline importer CLI (api/scripts/migrate/knowledge). Every org search now\nconsults orgId IN (caller, '_shared'); reads fall back org -> shared (org doc shadows shared).\nService writes REFUSE the shared actor (403). New knowledge_doc_map side table maps\n(orgId, collection, docId) -> fts rowid so index deletes are O(log n), not O(corpus);\nbulkIndexDocs() batches the 500k-doc import. The \"never pool across orgs\" rule keeps holding\nfor ORG data - the shared partition is a deliberate, read-only public spine, not org pooling."
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "annot-t3ndpud6ty3g",
      "x": 60,
      "y": 1044,
      "width": 748.8000000000001,
      "height": 90,
      "text": "AS-BUILT 2026-07-11 (integration builder): new persisted collection integration_builder_sessions\n(userId, orgId, integrationKey?, messages[], currentPackage?, validationErrors[]) - the builder\nchat survives restarts. Integration DEFINITIONS gain a runtime tier: <dataDir>/integrations/\nruntime/<key>/ (userCreated: true) shadowing the read-only baseline under api/assets/integrations;\nwritten only by the builder save route after server-side re-validation (reserved baseline keys refused).",
      "originalText": "AS-BUILT 2026-07-11 (integration builder): new persisted collection integration_builder_sessions\n(userId, orgId, integrationKey?, messages[], currentPackage?, validationErrors[]) - the builder\nchat survives restarts. Integration DEFINITIONS gain a runtime tier: <dataDir>/integrations/\nruntime/<key>/ (userCreated: true) shadowing the read-only baseline under api/assets/integrations;\nwritten only by the builder save route after server-side re-validation (reserved baseline keys refused).",
      "fontSize": 14,
