    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "annot-sheets-b1-20260717",
      "x": 70,
      "y": 1440,
      "width": 760,
      "height": 140,
      "text": "AS-BUILT 2026-07-17 (chat sheets, mega-run B1): sessions rows gain sheets[] SUBDOCUMENTS\n{ sheetId, title, createdFromMessageId, revisions[ { revisionId, content(markdown), createdAt,\neditedBy?, editSource: agent|user, instruction? } ] } - decision B.B, no new collection. Legacy\nsessions (no sheets field): readers derive one sheet per assistant message at READ time (no\nbackfill); a user rename/revision MATERIALISES the derived sheet on the session record first.\nModel-bound history collapses a sheet-spawning turn to its LATEST revision (agents/context.ts\napplyLatestSheetRevisions). Assistant message metadata now also carries provenance:\ntraceId (= runId) + memoriesUsed (layer-1 injection count).",
      "originalText": "AS-BUILT 2026-07-17 (chat sheets, mega-run B1): sessions rows gain sheets[] SUBDOCUMENTS\n{ sheetId, title, createdFromMessageId, revisions[ { revisionId, content(markdown), createdAt,\neditedBy?, editSource: agent|user, instruction? } ] } - decision B.B, no new collection. Legacy\nsessions (no sheets field): readers derive one sheet per assistant message at READ time (no\nbackfill); a user rename/revision MATERIALISES the derived sheet on the session record first.\nModel-bound history collapses a sheet-spawning turn to its LATEST revision (agents/context.ts\napplyLatestSheetRevisions). Assistant message metadata now also carries provenance:\ntraceId (= runId) + memoriesUsed (layer-1 injection count).",
      "rawText": "AS-BUILT 2026-07-17 (chat sheets, mega-run B1): sessions rows gain sheets[] SUBDOCUMENTS\n{ sheetId, title, createdFromMessageId, revisions[ { revisionId, content(markdown), createdAt,\neditedBy?, editSource: agent|user, instruction? } ] } - decision B.B, no new collection. Legacy\nsessions (no sheets field): readers derive one sheet per assistant message at READ time (no\nbackfill); a user rename/revision MATERIALISES the derived sheet on the session record first.\nModel-bound history collapses a sheet-spawning turn to its LATEST revision (agents/context.ts\napplyLatestSheetRevisions). Assistant message metadata now also carries provenance:\ntraceId (= runId) + memoriesUsed (layer-1 injection count).",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#b45309",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
